## Common Patterns

### Buttons

```erb
<%# GOOD - Native button with visible text %>
<%%= render Bali::Button::Component.new(name: 'Save Changes') %>

<%# GOOD - Icon button with aria-label %>
<%%= render Bali::Button::Component.new(
  icon: 'x',
  'aria-label': 'Close dialog'
) %>
```

### Forms

```erb
<%# Labels are automatically associated %>
<%%= f.bali_text_field :email,
  label: 'Email',
  hint: "We'll never share your email",
  error: @user.errors[:email].first
%>
```

### Modals

Bali's Modal component automatically includes:
- `role="dialog"`
- `aria-modal="true"`
- Focus trap within modal
- Return focus on close
- Escape key handling

